{"id": "ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 37, "displayName": {"text": "Kissa by Motto", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wNFZHNXRSRkZSUVd4NFFYWkVTbmt0TlVWb1VsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Kissa itself was very new comer to the neighborhood, but not the case with Motto Tea, which probably a lot of people have been very familiar with. Loving the concept that totally reminded me of Japanese / Korean coffee shop concept with a twist of Boho, nature, and vintage blended in together.\n\nThe chic yet cozy venue obviously drew the crowd interest and even visiting amidst a week day still exposed me to bit of a crowd. All the servers were super friendly and patient, answering my questions on what they offered and letting me taking my time to make my decision, but just one drawback was it took them pretty long to get the drinks ready.\n\nThey seemed to be popular for the roll cake and basque cheesecake, but the various canelé flavors triggered my interest more so I opted for the Double Matcha canelé. Unfortunately I might not be a fan of the canelé base itself as it lacked the fragrant buttery flavor I fancied in a canelé and I did wish the texture was more chewy inside. The matcha cream on top was nice in balancing the sweetness, especially with the stuffing being bit on the bitter side.\n\nI got their Jasmine Matcha, which I thought come at decent price compared to similar ones in LA. It was so-so to me flavor wise. Decent but probably nothing distinctive that made it stand out. Perhaps I should give a try on either their specialty latte or cream top drinks next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Kissa itself was very new comer to the neighborhood, but not the case with Motto Tea, which probably a lot of people have been very familiar with. Loving the concept that totally reminded me of Japanese / Korean coffee shop concept with a twist of Boho, nature, and vintage blended in together.\n\nThe chic yet cozy venue obviously drew the crowd interest and even visiting amidst a week day still exposed me to bit of a crowd. All the servers were super friendly and patient, answering my questions on what they offered and letting me taking my time to make my decision, but just one drawback was it took them pretty long to get the drinks ready.\n\nThey seemed to be popular for the roll cake and basque cheesecake, but the various canelé flavors triggered my interest more so I opted for the Double Matcha canelé. Unfortunately I might not be a fan of the canelé base itself as it lacked the fragrant buttery flavor I fancied in a canelé and I did wish the texture was more chewy inside. The matcha cream on top was nice in balancing the sweetness, especially with the stuffing being bit on the bitter side.\n\nI got their Jasmine Matcha, which I thought come at decent price compared to similar ones in LA. It was so-so to me flavor wise. Decent but probably nothing distinctive that made it stand out. Perhaps I should give a try on either their specialty latte or cream top drinks next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "JG", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111257583310582062343/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8UqbsVHg2VxS0LgD7ECyFYYeCZ3BA4Dt0ktxf3VxgqHOQs4o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-01T22:22:00.494360650Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wNFZHNXRSRkZSUVd4NFFYWkVTbmt0TlVWb1VsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wNFZHNXRSRkZSUVd4NFFYWkVTbmt0TlVWb1VsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c34c3169660f:0x62fcd583f9f8b4df"}, {"name": "places/ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxUlUxUjNibXhtTWtscE5XSnpjV3hqUVd4ZlpYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Soft opening: Very cute overall vibes~\nThe pistachio cloudy latte was delicious. And there aren’t any decaf options so far but the cafe latte tasted great as well.\n\nThe cakes from motto are some of my favorites so I'm excited they're opening up a designated store for them.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Soft opening: Very cute overall vibes~\nThe pistachio cloudy latte was delicious. And there aren’t any decaf options so far but the cafe latte tasted great as well.\n\nThe cakes from motto are some of my favorites so I'm excited they're opening up a designated store for them.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Joy G", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107466164501517504226/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNPTCL_9QyNhdtYpL8kXrqmi17mfXoaYMoIsBkAWZm9aPjr9Kz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-10T22:52:23.526780958Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxUlUxUjNibXhtTWtscE5XSnpjV3hqUVd4ZlpYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxUlUxUjNibXhtTWtscE5XSnpjV3hqUVd4ZlpYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c34c3169660f:0x62fcd583f9f8b4df"}, {"name": "places/ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwYVUzTnNhWFp1WVd0VWJWa3lhVVJmVjJKSVdWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It's such an adorable Cafe to chill and hangout with your friends at!!! 🥺💞 Tried the Nutellamisu Cloud Latte the first time I went, then the Jasmine Matcha Latte the second time... BOTH WERE ABSOLUTELY DELICIOUSSS💞💞💞", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It's such an adorable Cafe to chill and hangout with your friends at!!! 🥺💞 Tried the Nutellamisu Cloud Latte the first time I went, then the Jasmine Matcha Latte the second time... BOTH WERE ABSOLUTELY DELICIOUSSS💞💞💞", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Angela Yan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104067728000504612204/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWD05UavOdgUZjd1YS9X528AW9vx0HRNvm4NPz-5ql7wC4Fr1Sm=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-11T06:17:21.212907907Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwYVUzTnNhWFp1WVd0VWJWa3lhVVJmVjJKSVdWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwYVUzTnNhWFp1WVd0VWJWa3lhVVJmVjJKSVdWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c34c3169660f:0x62fcd583f9f8b4df"}, {"name": "places/ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OT2RqUkhVa3A2TlRGcGJVOVBXVk56VGxaWVIwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is truly a neighborhood gem, I love all their specialty drink, especially their Yuzu Espresso Tonic. Their pour over is so also amazing, I can taste multiple layer and flavor for their pour over.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is truly a neighborhood gem, I love all their specialty drink, especially their Yuzu Espresso Tonic. Their pour over is so also amazing, I can taste multiple layer and flavor for their pour over.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nelly Lyu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113547181267681067675/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHLU7-4OvY1d6K5-Qn0HEwwVHLLCWcJn4Zx1Qo_sJb9v2hJw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-11T00:19:13.395090587Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OT2RqUkhVa3A2TlRGcGJVOVBXVk56VGxaWVIwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OT2RqUkhVa3A2TlRGcGJVOVBXVk56VGxaWVIwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c34c3169660f:0x62fcd583f9f8b4df"}, {"name": "places/ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNVVXSTRaMUpYUVdaS2VVZFRaRzFaTms1dk5XYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Extremely cutely-designed, rustic interior! Everything about the ambiance feels beautifully down-to-earth, unique, and intentional. I ordered the Kyoto Latte, which had a lovely balance of cream and sweetness that didn’t overpower the core brew. Service was also very friendly and helpful with information. Very lovely experience overall — I’ll be coming back in the future to try the cute pastries!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Extremely cutely-designed, rustic interior! Everything about the ambiance feels beautifully down-to-earth, unique, and intentional. I ordered the Kyoto Latte, which had a lovely balance of cream and sweetness that didn’t overpower the core brew. Service was also very friendly and helpful with information. Very lovely experience overall — I’ll be coming back in the future to try the cute pastries!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Keli Fisher", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107977192155573615137/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCDjqOC1Jg0HVxezmi1d9xeI4P1ybWsNO6FaBlGSgkI72nnk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-10T20:54:34.676849212Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNVVXSTRaMUpYUVdaS2VVZFRaRzFaTms1dk5XYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNVVXSTRaMUpYUVdaS2VVZFRaRzFaTms1dk5XYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c34c3169660f:0x62fcd583f9f8b4df"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJD2ZpMUzDwoAR37T4-YPV_GI/photos/AWCwydg7QNbJVr0rqWjVwSa1NLFvOOm5kCH2iDQFWwZJ2pTrKKkuNEOlM3smKeJpbyDF